## Please take half a minute of your time to read this short disclaimer
shaweelAddons-v2 is still a work in progress. **It is not done.** Even though it is downloadable through Actions, that does not mean it is yet meant for public use. Expect bugs and all kinds of issues.
# shaweelAddons-v2
A legit Fabric 1.21.10 QOL mod for Hypixel Skyblock mainly focused at Dungeons made primarly for my personal use but also published here on GitHub for anyone to download, use, modify, contribute or fork.

